Usage
-----

This is a simple extension for Gnome 3 that display a pop-up 
with current date and time when you move the mouse to the
bottom of the screen.

Installation
------------

Copy the extension folder to:

/home/anton/.local/share/gnome-shell/extensions/

Then restart the Gnome shell, for example, by pressing
ALT+F2, then type "r" and press enter.

